videos.description: Tariq Owens rejects Missouri's Kassius Robertson layup attempt in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Plays St. Johns (Owens rejects Robertson at the rim for St. John's) 2017/11/24

videos.headline: Owens rejects Robertson at the rim for St. John's

videos.description: Tariq Owens finds Shamorie Ponds on a backdoor cut for a bucket for St. John's.
videos.headline: Ponds and Owens connect for backdoor layup

videos.description: Shamorie Ponds buries a deep three pointer to beat the shot clock to cut the margin to single digits for St. John's.
videos.headline: Ponds beats the clock with a deep 3 for St. John's

videos.description: Justin Simon three pointer ties the game 44-44 for the Red Storm to erase at 16-point deficit in the second half.
videos.headline: Simon corner 3 ties it for St. John's

videos.description: Tariq Owens slams home the alley opp feed to increase the lead for St. John's.
videos.headline: Owens dunk off alley oop from Simon

videos.description: Justin Simon dunks home the alley oop feed from Shamorie Ponds to give St. John's the lead.
videos.headline: Simon dunk off alley oop from Ponds

videos.description: Jontay Porter banks home a 3 to increase the lead for the Tigers.
